{
  "stem": "18626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 28.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They pushed him in the there, and they burned with the house, the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "With-- not-- with a lot of more other people were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sick people, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "People who couldn't walk on the march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So he walked in in that house there on the left side of the gate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what exactly it was in that house there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was administration or something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the-- while we we were walking, the house was burning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that's how we were walking all the way to the railroad under heavy guard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And while we were walking under heavy guard, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and this time the guard was real heavy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was no plain rifles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was machine guns they had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "All the green uniform SS or NKVD.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I don't know what department of the German army it was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "NKVD, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It's like the SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The sad situation was while we were taken to the railroad, the German army, the Wehrmacht, was retreating too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They were already being chased by the Soviet Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were going to the railroad, and the German army was running for their lives to save themselves, the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I've seen, like I told you before, the shiny German army who I thought they were going to take the world with the shiny boots, drinking the champagne, with the uniforms, being kissed by the Lithuanian girls.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I've seen the same German army running without boots, crawling, dirty, torn clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They were laying on the sidewalks and on the streets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I heard with my own ears while going through, the officer told one of the German soldiers from the Wehrmacht, in German, get up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Don't forget.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "You are a German soldier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Shame on you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Up!",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
